string.name: data_type_separator
string.description: Separator (comma and whitespace in English) for a potentially long list of data type names listed in data access entry, as in 'Write: Steps, Distance, Calories'. [CHAR_LIMIT=NONE]

string.name: sleep_stage_default
string.description: Label that shows sleep session duration.[CHAR LIMIT=80]

string.name: hour_minute_duration_accessibility
string.translation_description: Hour and minute time duration representation used by accessibility, 'space' between minute and second should be deleted or replaced according to each language to translate [CHAR LIMIT=NONE]

string.name: vitamin_a
string.description: Vitamin A, also known as retinol, is key for good vision, a healthy immune system, and cell growth. [CHAR LIMIT=50]

string.name: vitamin_b12
string.description: Vitamin B12, also known as cobalamin, is a water-soluble vitamin involved in metabolism. [CHAR LIMIT=50]

string.name: vitamin_b6
string.description: Vitamin B6 is one of the B vitamins, and thus an essential nutrient. [CHAR LIMIT=50]

string.name: vitamin_c
string.description: Vitamin C is a water-soluble vitamin found in various foods and sold as a dietary supplement. [CHAR LIMIT=50]

string.name: vitamin_d
string.description: Vitamin D helps regulate the amount of calcium and phosphate in the body. [CHAR LIMIT=50]

string.name: vitamin_e
string.description: Vitamin E is an important fat-soluble nutrient. It's a powerful antioxidant and is needed for immune health and cellular signaling in your body. [CHAR LIMIT=50]

string.name: vitamin_k
string.description: Vitamin K is a group of vitamins that the body needs for blood clotting, helping wounds to heal. [CHAR LIMIT=50]

string.name: nutrient_with_value
string.description: Used for formatting nutrition data. Example: Copper: 29g [CHAR LIMIT=50]

string.name: stone_pound_short_label
string.translation_description: Weight in stone and pounds. Example: 9st 2lb. [ICU][CHAR LIMIT=60]

string.name: stone_pound_long_label
string.translation_description: Weight in stone and pounds representation used by accessibility. Example: 9 stone, 2 pounds. [ICU][CHAR LIMIT=60]

string.name: temperature_celsius
string.description: Temperature value with unit. [ICU SYNTAX][CHAR LIMIT=80]

string.name: temperature_kelvin
string.description: Temperature value with unit. [ICU SYNTAX][CHAR LIMIT=80]

string.name: temperature_fahrenheit
string.description: Temperature value with unit. [ICU SYNTAX][CHAR LIMIT=80]

string.name: feet_inches_format
string.translation_description: Format for displaying height in feet and inches in compacted form e.g. 5′11″ [CHAR LIMIT=10]

string.name: feet_inches_format_long
string.translation_description: Format for displaying height in feet and inches in long form e.g. 5 feet 11 inches [CHAR LIMIT=60]

string.name: percent
string.description: Percentage value with unit. [ICU SYNTAX][CHAR LIMIT=80]

string.name: playstore_app_title
string.description: Navigates to the Play Store and shows a collection of apps compatible with Health Connect [CHAR_LIMIT=40]

string.name: date_owner_format
string.description: Format for displaying a date attributed to the data and the name of the application the data comes from. Example: Mon 13 Jun - Nokia Health Mate. [CHAR LIMIT=NONE]
